f(0) = 7
f(n+1) = f(n) + 6n + 1
n => 0 
f(n) = 3n^2 + 2n + 7
f(n+1)=f(n)+6n+1\Rightarrow f(n+1)-f(n)=6n+1
f(1)-f(0)=6.0+1\\ f(2)-f(1)=6.1+1\\ f(3)-f(2)=6.2+1\\ ---------\\ ---------\\ ---------\\ f(n)-f(n-1)=6.(n-1)+1
f(n)-f(0)=6\{0+1+2+........+(n-1)\}+n.1\\ f(n)-f(0)=6\frac{(n-1)(n-1+1)}{2}+n\\ f(n)=f(0)+6\frac{(n-1)n}{2}+n\\ f(n)=7+3n^2-3n+n\\ f(n)=3n^2-2n+7
f(n) = f(n) - f(n-1) + f(n-1) - f(n-2) + ... + f(1) - f(0) + f(0)
 = 6(n-1) + 1 + + 6(n -2) + 1 + ... + 6*0 + 1 + 7 
= 6*(n-1)*n/2 + n + 7 
= 3n(n - 1) + n + 7 
= 3n^2 - 2n + 7
